short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds links to the research with GPT chatbot, to get chatting easily.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Research With GPT Chatbot Extension is a Chrome browser extension that enhances your ArXiv browsing experience by allowing you to seamlessly access ResearchWithGPT's chatbot feature from ArXiv pages. With this extension, you can easily generate chatbot queries based on the ArXiv paper you are reading.
